---
title: Honey-Gochujang Halloumi Steak with Sesame Chips and Avocado Salad
description: Discover a new way to serve up halloumi by slicing it into a thick 'steak' for a hearty vegetarian meal. Glazed with honey and spicy-sweet gochujang, we're serving it with sesame chips and an avocado salad for an Asian inspired twist on veggie steak night.
